stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    
    Idle --> Triggered: User Action
    Triggered --> Evaluating: Check Criteria
    Evaluating --> Unlocked: Criteria Met
    Evaluating --> Idle: Criteria Not Met
    Unlocked --> Celebrating: Show Animation
    Celebrating --> Rewarding: Grant XP/Badge
    Rewarding --> Shared: Optional Share
    Shared --> [*]
    Rewarding --> [*]
    
    note right of Triggered
        Examples:
        - Command used 10x
        - Project completed
        - 7-day streak
        - Helped 5 users
    end note
    
    note right of Celebrating
        Confetti animation
        Sound effect
        Notification
        Dashboard update
    end note